WEBVTT

01:32.270 --> 01:34.930
[How dare you!?]

01:35.030 --> 01:37.820
[Episode 10]

01:40.910 --> 01:42.710
Which company are you the CEO of?

01:43.770 --> 01:45.350
What does this company do?

01:45.509 --> 01:46.570
When was it listed?

01:47.590 --> 01:48.850
What was its market cap

01:50.870 --> 01:52.200
before you came here?

01:53.590 --> 01:55.430
I should just tell her everything.

01:55.430 --> 01:56.560
Who exactly are you?

01:58.380 --> 01:59.979
But if I tell the whole truth,

02:00.980 --> 02:03.820
that fragile bit of trust and closeness
she has with me

02:03.820 --> 02:05.080
will probably vanish.

02:08.280 --> 02:11.210
Between letting her doubt me
and breaking her heart,

02:12.080 --> 02:14.140
I would rather let her keep doubting.

02:28.079 --> 02:29.079
I don't remember.

02:46.050 --> 02:47.579
If you don't want to tell me,

02:51.620 --> 02:52.620
I won't ask again.

03:10.590 --> 03:11.310
Your Highness!

03:11.310 --> 03:12.000
Your Highness!

03:12.000 --> 03:13.710
Wake up! Wake up!

03:16.710 --> 03:17.570
Your Highness,

03:17.640 --> 03:18.670
stop sleeping.

03:18.710 --> 03:21.570
The Empress Dowager
is here to check your homework.

03:46.000 --> 03:47.000
What the hell?

03:47.680 --> 03:49.190
What am I wearing?

03:50.000 --> 03:51.750
How did I wake up here?

03:53.520 --> 03:54.870
Where am I?

03:56.180 --> 03:57.270
I think earlier

03:57.470 --> 03:59.470
I was sneaking my phone in math class

04:00.190 --> 04:02.710
and accidentally clicked
on a cheesy web novel

04:02.710 --> 04:03.310
called...

04:05.190 --> 04:06.030
Oh right.

04:06.670 --> 04:10.070
It's called "Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort"!

04:11.150 --> 04:13.010
The Empress Dowager has arrived!

04:16.190 --> 04:16.990
Your Majesty.

04:18.000 --> 04:20.130
How is the Crown Prince's study today?

04:20.870 --> 04:21.950
Your Majesty,

04:22.480 --> 04:25.310
today the Crown Prince studied
the Thousand Character Classic

04:25.310 --> 04:29.300
and learned about astronomy, geography,
and social customs.

04:29.510 --> 04:32.240
-Devil's Favorite Concubine?
-He is a quick and eager learner

04:32.240 --> 04:33.150
-Favorite Consort?
-and has already

04:33.150 --> 04:34.560
grasped much of the material.

04:34.560 --> 04:37.220
So it really is a story
set in an imperial palace.

04:37.630 --> 04:38.630
It's just that...

04:39.690 --> 04:40.480
Oh no.

04:41.120 --> 04:42.240
How do I get back?

04:46.510 --> 04:47.590
It hurts so much?

04:48.190 --> 04:48.520
Here,

04:50.750 --> 04:52.150
let me massage it for you.

04:52.870 --> 04:53.200
Here.

04:54.250 --> 04:55.580
Don't touch me, Mr. Bei.

04:56.040 --> 04:57.900
Why did it flare up all of a sudden?

04:58.290 --> 04:59.640
It might be a brain tumor.

04:59.640 --> 05:00.380
Impossible.

05:00.590 --> 05:01.790
I checked your pulse.

05:01.870 --> 05:02.810
You don't have that.

05:02.810 --> 05:04.090
I need a CT scan.

05:04.840 --> 05:05.970
Wh-What T?

05:10.070 --> 05:10.730
Never mind.

05:18.360 --> 05:18.950
Mr. Bei.

05:20.360 --> 05:21.620
I want sweet porridge.

05:21.630 --> 05:22.070
Okay.

05:22.430 --> 05:23.680
I'll go make some right now.

05:23.680 --> 05:24.360
Just wait.

05:33.390 --> 05:35.159
Your Majesty, Mr. Bai sent another letter,

05:35.159 --> 05:36.680
urging you to get rid of
the demonic consort as soon as possible.

05:36.680 --> 05:37.750
She is not a demonic consort!

05:37.750 --> 05:39.080
No need to reply to that!

05:39.400 --> 05:39.870
Yes.

05:46.340 --> 05:47.200
Your Highness,

05:47.320 --> 05:49.340
His Majesty didn't summon you today.

05:49.340 --> 05:51.680
Is it appropriate for us
to go there directly?

05:51.680 --> 05:53.510
It's precisely because he didn't summon me

05:53.510 --> 05:54.680
that I must go.

05:55.500 --> 05:56.330
Why?

05:56.450 --> 05:57.580
I don't understand.

05:58.840 --> 06:01.950
I, Xie Yong'er, am the chosen one.

06:03.030 --> 06:04.250
In this world, I was supposed to

06:04.250 --> 06:05.720
have everything go my way.

06:07.070 --> 06:08.380
But I've been in the palace for so long.

06:08.380 --> 06:10.310
Not only have I accomplished nothing,

06:10.310 --> 06:12.360
but I have also been treated
like an outcast.

06:12.360 --> 06:13.020
An outcast?

06:14.780 --> 06:16.840
Now, although he says he believes me,

06:17.390 --> 06:19.800
he hasn't summoned me
to attend him even once since then.

06:19.800 --> 06:21.430
Don't you think something's off?

06:21.430 --> 06:23.060
So, you mean...

06:24.780 --> 06:25.710
Ling, remember,

06:26.630 --> 06:27.780
in this harem,

06:28.630 --> 06:30.890
one careless step can cost you your life.

06:32.870 --> 06:33.430
Tonight,

06:34.000 --> 06:35.220
I must see His Majesty

06:35.500 --> 06:37.100
and get to the bottom of this.

06:39.810 --> 06:43.120
[Yongyan Hall]

06:43.930 --> 06:45.870
Eunuch An, I need to see His Majesty.

06:45.870 --> 06:47.470
Please let His Majesty know.

06:48.920 --> 06:49.780
Your Highness,

06:50.190 --> 06:52.040
His Majesty's headache has flared up.

06:52.040 --> 06:54.370
It's not convenient for him to see anyone.

06:54.630 --> 06:55.270
Eunuch An,

06:55.680 --> 06:57.400
if His Majesty is unwell,

06:57.510 --> 07:00.360
then all the more reason for me
to go in and attend him.

07:00.360 --> 07:02.430
Your Highness, please go back.

07:02.870 --> 07:04.760
His Majesty is seeing no one tonight.

07:04.760 --> 07:05.450
Please,

07:05.750 --> 07:07.750
don't make things difficult for me.

07:18.080 --> 07:21.310
[Yongyan Hall]

07:26.950 --> 07:29.430
Having everything go my way?

07:30.750 --> 07:33.210
Is this how you treat the chosen one?

07:46.140 --> 07:47.159
Why is she here?

07:47.710 --> 07:50.040
And she looks even more miserable than me.

07:52.200 --> 07:52.870
Oh right.

07:53.010 --> 07:54.860
She's fallen out of favor
with His Majesty.

07:54.860 --> 07:57.190
Then let me make things
even worse for you.

07:58.950 --> 08:00.080
Go back first, Ling.

08:00.510 --> 08:01.040
Okay.

08:19.680 --> 08:21.410
Sister, why are you here alone?

08:22.120 --> 08:23.580
Are you enjoying the rain?

08:24.120 --> 08:24.830
Yong'er?

08:25.510 --> 08:26.440
Why are you here?

08:29.830 --> 08:31.490
I just went to see His Majesty,

08:32.669 --> 08:34.799
but I didn't even get through the door.

08:35.960 --> 08:38.020
It seems his headache flared up

08:38.390 --> 08:39.850
and he's not feeling well.

08:42.370 --> 08:43.429
His Majesty is ill?

08:44.300 --> 08:45.230
You didn't know?

08:51.440 --> 08:52.020
Sister.

08:53.500 --> 08:56.410
I know you and His Majesty are in love.

08:57.370 --> 08:59.100
I think this is the perfect time

08:59.390 --> 09:01.910
for you two to patch things up.

09:02.080 --> 09:03.540
Why don't you give it a try?

09:04.840 --> 09:06.100
Since that's the case,

09:06.990 --> 09:08.050
I'll go take a look.

09:08.510 --> 09:10.620
Thank you for coming
to tell me about this.

09:10.620 --> 09:11.240
Go now.

09:22.180 --> 09:24.180
His Majesty said he's seeing no one.

09:24.590 --> 09:26.320
You're just going to hit a wall.

09:28.630 --> 09:32.280
[Yongyan Hall]

09:47.720 --> 09:48.120
Dan.

09:48.750 --> 09:49.120
Dan?

09:50.030 --> 09:50.940
Wanyin is here.

09:51.870 --> 09:53.130
The porridge is ready.

09:54.600 --> 09:55.530
Thanks, Mr. Bei.

09:55.960 --> 09:56.420
Well...

09:58.030 --> 09:58.760
You two talk.

09:59.600 --> 10:00.330
You two talk.

10:11.460 --> 10:12.390
Let me feed you.

10:19.780 --> 10:20.530
Let's talk.

10:22.840 --> 10:24.140
There's no rush.

10:24.410 --> 10:25.540
You should rest now.

10:26.150 --> 10:27.210
You guessed right.

10:29.470 --> 10:31.110
I'm not actually a CEO.

10:37.890 --> 10:38.950
Before I came here,

10:39.650 --> 10:41.050
I was a third-rate actor.

10:42.270 --> 10:43.800
I played bit parts for years

10:44.290 --> 10:45.490
and never made it big.

10:47.840 --> 10:49.320
If that's all,

10:50.080 --> 10:51.320
why did you lie to me?

10:51.940 --> 10:53.400
I didn't mean to lie to you.

10:55.050 --> 10:56.910
You first guessed that I was a CEO.

10:57.470 --> 11:00.600
You're not one of those
legendary alpha bosses, are you?

11:00.720 --> 11:02.120
I just went along with it.

11:04.000 --> 11:05.060
Why did you do that?

11:07.150 --> 11:07.960
I...

11:10.080 --> 11:11.480
have always had bad luck,

11:12.480 --> 11:14.840
and I don't seem
to have any real talent either.

11:14.840 --> 11:16.360
I thought I would die here.

11:18.550 --> 11:19.240
Then,

11:22.870 --> 11:23.670
you showed up,

11:27.090 --> 11:28.820
like a savior from the heavens,

11:30.030 --> 11:31.150
holding the script

11:32.590 --> 11:33.850
and determined to win.

11:37.550 --> 11:38.680
When I looked at you,

11:39.770 --> 11:40.720
I finally felt

11:43.150 --> 11:45.210
that there might still be hope for me.

11:56.370 --> 11:57.630
You're a little...

11:58.630 --> 12:00.360
different from how I imagined.

12:02.080 --> 12:03.060
I thought

12:03.870 --> 12:06.200
you were carrying some deep, dark secret.

12:10.590 --> 12:11.640
Now you know.

12:12.510 --> 12:14.110
I don't have much of a chance.

12:14.420 --> 12:16.480
Even if Prince Duan is a 2D character,

12:16.780 --> 12:18.780
he's 100 times more capable than me.

12:19.260 --> 12:20.460
So that promise

12:20.910 --> 12:21.710
still stands.

12:25.150 --> 12:26.280
If you want to leave,

12:28.010 --> 12:29.470
I completely understand.

12:29.950 --> 12:30.880
I won't stop you.

12:37.690 --> 12:39.320
Even if you don't act pitiful,

12:39.320 --> 12:40.240
I won't leave.

12:43.110 --> 12:44.730
You need to get better soon.

12:45.530 --> 12:46.700
Our future plans

12:46.720 --> 12:48.450
still need your acting skills.

12:55.980 --> 12:57.510
Why are your clothes all wet?

12:57.510 --> 12:58.860
I just got caught in a bit of rain.

12:58.860 --> 13:00.200
I'll go back and change.

13:00.380 --> 13:01.200
Why don't you

13:01.230 --> 13:02.360
take a hot bath here?

13:07.270 --> 13:08.480
If you catch a cold,

13:09.020 --> 13:11.420
who's going to take care of me,
the patient?

13:53.670 --> 13:56.520
[Xiao Tiancai]

13:59.800 --> 14:01.260
Which palace are you from?

14:01.510 --> 14:03.240
Don't stand in this heavy rain.

14:03.240 --> 14:05.570
Go into the flower house and take shelter.

14:05.910 --> 14:07.770
What are you waiting for? Go on in.

14:11.240 --> 14:11.770
Hurry up.

14:21.960 --> 14:24.620
Wait until the rain lets up
before you head back.

14:25.330 --> 14:26.460
Take this umbrella.

14:29.020 --> 14:30.950
Don't get caught in the rain again.

14:32.280 --> 14:33.340
If you catch a cold,

14:33.390 --> 14:34.850
at best you'll get a fever,

14:35.290 --> 14:37.450
and at worst it could affect
your internal organs.

14:37.450 --> 14:38.980
That would be real trouble.

14:41.540 --> 14:42.470
This is mugwort.

14:42.830 --> 14:44.200
Take it back and smoke this spot,

14:44.200 --> 14:45.200
the Fengchi point.

14:45.200 --> 14:46.480
It helps dispel cold and dampness.

14:46.480 --> 14:47.880
It's best not to get sick.

15:02.240 --> 15:02.970
What is this?

15:05.030 --> 15:06.360
This is called danggui.

15:06.840 --> 15:09.100
It grows along the northwestern border.

15:09.220 --> 15:09.770
Some time ago,

15:09.770 --> 15:10.470
the Imperial Hospital wanted

15:10.470 --> 15:12.670
to compile a catalog of medicinal herbs

15:12.720 --> 15:15.340
and study their effects
and growing conditions,

15:15.340 --> 15:18.670
so they had people bring back
a few plants from the northwest

15:18.830 --> 15:20.090
and planted them here.

15:20.680 --> 15:22.560
They were fresh and lovely at first

15:22.560 --> 15:24.090
and grew a lot in just 3 days.

15:25.110 --> 15:26.320
But for some reason,

15:27.150 --> 15:29.480
after they bloomed, they began to wither.

15:31.750 --> 15:33.440
The same species can be very different

15:33.440 --> 15:35.040
in different environments.

15:35.790 --> 15:37.050
The northwest is cold.

15:37.600 --> 15:38.730
If you plant it here,

15:40.030 --> 15:41.430
it surely won't survive.

15:45.080 --> 15:46.540
That's not entirely true.

15:46.840 --> 15:48.000
Plants are like people.

15:48.000 --> 15:49.460
They have strong vitality

15:49.480 --> 15:51.790
and will try hard
to adapt to different environments.

15:51.790 --> 15:53.240
Dandelions take root wherever they land.

15:53.240 --> 15:54.630
Wild grass grows back stronger
after burning.

15:54.630 --> 15:57.260
Sometimes the price of survival

15:57.550 --> 15:59.030
is not being as lush as before,

15:59.030 --> 16:00.430
or bearing fewer fruits,

16:00.560 --> 16:02.290
but that's the law of survival.

16:02.600 --> 16:03.330
Look at that.

16:03.440 --> 16:04.040
Lilyturf.

16:04.520 --> 16:06.320
It's also known as the "immortal herb."

16:06.320 --> 16:07.720
Whether it's dry or damp,

16:07.870 --> 16:08.780
warm or cold,

16:09.030 --> 16:10.290
it survives just fine.

16:11.400 --> 16:12.860
That's easy for you to say.

16:13.460 --> 16:15.060
With a flick of your fingers,

16:15.130 --> 16:17.130
you decide whether it lives or dies.

16:17.510 --> 16:19.910
But has anyone ever asked
if it was willing?

16:20.270 --> 16:22.330
Maybe death is its way of protesting.

16:25.480 --> 16:27.640
It... it's just a plant.

16:28.230 --> 16:29.360
Miss, can you tell me

16:29.960 --> 16:32.150
how you know whether it's willing or not?

16:32.150 --> 16:33.460
I just feel

16:34.360 --> 16:36.760
it shouldn't have been taken away
from home

16:37.200 --> 16:39.660
to grow
in this completely unfamiliar place

16:39.910 --> 16:40.970
and wither here.

16:41.630 --> 16:42.760
What did it do wrong?

16:43.320 --> 16:45.180
Why should it go through all this?

16:47.810 --> 16:49.100
You have a soft heart.

16:50.670 --> 16:51.870
It pains me deeply

16:52.360 --> 16:53.820
that they didn't survive.

16:54.240 --> 16:56.520
I come every day
to mist them and cool them down.

16:56.520 --> 16:58.030
I even prepare ice every day

16:58.030 --> 17:00.510
to recreate a cold,
damp environment for them.

17:00.510 --> 17:02.110
Though they suffer greatly,

17:02.270 --> 17:03.330
they aren't alone,

17:03.630 --> 17:06.030
nor are they facing all this
by themselves.

17:06.030 --> 17:06.790
If,

17:07.640 --> 17:08.960
as you say,

17:09.349 --> 17:10.130
they truly

17:10.550 --> 17:12.079
have thoughts of their own,

17:12.650 --> 17:14.510
then seeing someone watch over them

17:14.510 --> 17:15.880
and make an effort for them

17:15.880 --> 17:18.339
might give them a bit more will
to keep going.

17:24.430 --> 17:26.690
Even a herb has someone watching over it,

17:26.920 --> 17:28.920
going through hardships together.

17:29.560 --> 17:31.750
Yet I have always been alone.

17:42.170 --> 17:43.500
Are you feeling better?

17:43.790 --> 17:44.720
I ate something,

17:44.880 --> 17:45.940
and I'm better now.

17:47.110 --> 17:47.590
Well,

17:49.110 --> 17:50.510
if there's nothing else,

17:51.110 --> 17:52.160
I'll go back now.

17:53.730 --> 17:55.930
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

17:56.140 --> 17:57.720
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

17:57.720 --> 17:58.270
What's wrong?

17:57.730 --> 17:59.890
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

17:58.780 --> 18:00.250
Is your head hurting again?

18:00.250 --> 18:01.670
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

18:00.830 --> 18:01.720
It's starting to hurt again.

18:01.720 --> 18:04.040
♪ Words unspoken ♪

18:04.720 --> 18:05.640
Why don't you stay?

18:05.640 --> 18:08.080
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

18:07.880 --> 18:09.140
Your hair is still wet,

18:09.760 --> 18:11.940
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

18:09.940 --> 18:11.400
and it's raining outside.

18:12.240 --> 18:13.570
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

18:13.780 --> 18:15.740
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

18:13.960 --> 18:14.360
But...

18:15.400 --> 18:17.680
But I'm supposed to be playing
the out-of-favor role right now.

18:16.260 --> 18:17.610
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

18:17.720 --> 18:20.130
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

18:18.270 --> 18:20.160
It wouldn't be appropriate for me to stay.

18:20.160 --> 18:21.490
Then let's just treat it

18:21.720 --> 18:25.160
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

18:22.070 --> 18:23.000
as a day off.

18:24.250 --> 18:26.500
Forget about the tyrant
and the demonic consort.

18:25.660 --> 18:29.050
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

18:26.830 --> 18:29.630
Forget about Prince Duan
and the Empress Dowager.

18:29.720 --> 18:32.780
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

18:32.200 --> 18:33.130
Just for one day.

18:33.140 --> 18:35.090
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

18:33.160 --> 18:33.720
Okay?

18:35.270 --> 18:37.000
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

18:37.210 --> 18:39.070
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

18:39.220 --> 18:41.320
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

18:41.800 --> 18:44.950
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

18:45.770 --> 18:48.100
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

18:48.170 --> 18:49.310
♪ Still unchanged ♪

18:49.780 --> 18:52.590
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

18:53.240 --> 18:54.800
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

18:54.800 --> 18:59.180
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

19:02.150 --> 19:03.980
Then let's stop thinking about anything

19:03.980 --> 19:05.180
and have a good sleep.

19:13.610 --> 19:17.140
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

19:17.690 --> 19:20.630
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

19:21.220 --> 19:23.290
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

19:23.290 --> 19:25.020
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

19:25.270 --> 19:27.130
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

19:27.230 --> 19:29.340
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

19:29.770 --> 19:32.980
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

19:33.750 --> 19:36.160
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

19:35.650 --> 19:36.280
Goodnight.

19:36.280 --> 19:37.340
♪ Still unchanged ♪

19:37.790 --> 19:40.700
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

19:41.250 --> 19:42.760
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

19:42.760 --> 19:50.110
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

20:02.650 --> 20:05.450
That fire in the library last time
was terrifying.

20:05.840 --> 20:07.840
Although it's being renovated now,

20:08.200 --> 20:09.750
safety isn't guaranteed.

20:10.440 --> 20:11.500
If you ask me,

20:11.870 --> 20:14.000
My Lady, you shouldn't have come here.

20:14.020 --> 20:15.100
It's fine.

20:15.370 --> 20:16.920
Isn't Madam Bei at the door?

20:17.150 --> 20:18.410
It's absolutely safe.

20:18.520 --> 20:20.790
The history of Yan State is so convoluted.

20:20.790 --> 20:22.520
And it has nothing to do with us.

20:23.350 --> 20:25.750
My Lady,
be careful not to strain your eyes.

20:26.320 --> 20:27.370
It's fine.

20:27.390 --> 20:28.850
My eyesight is excellent.

20:30.110 --> 20:33.160
My Lady, are you even listening to me?

20:33.960 --> 20:34.690
Take a break.

20:35.030 --> 20:36.160
Look at the scenery.

20:36.880 --> 20:37.680
My Lady, look.

20:38.350 --> 20:41.410
The hydrangeas in the field
are blooming beautifully.

20:51.780 --> 20:52.380
What's...

20:53.000 --> 20:53.760
going on?

20:54.270 --> 20:55.720
-Beautiful, right?
-SOS?

20:55.720 --> 20:58.580
It's just that the arrangement
looks a bit strange.

20:58.710 --> 20:59.190
Mei.

20:59.980 --> 21:00.670
Do you know

21:00.960 --> 21:02.490
who planted these flowers?

21:03.120 --> 21:04.080
I don't know.

21:04.360 --> 21:05.360
Put the book back.

21:05.370 --> 21:06.430
I'll go take a look.

21:09.030 --> 21:09.650
Wanyin!

21:09.820 --> 21:10.270
Wan...

21:12.360 --> 21:12.840
Mei!

21:13.030 --> 21:14.030
Get the umbrella!

21:14.050 --> 21:14.570
Go!

21:22.850 --> 21:29.640
[SOS]

21:24.810 --> 21:25.330
This...

21:26.820 --> 21:29.150
Could this be planted by a transmigrator?

21:29.450 --> 21:30.110
In Devil's Favorite Concubine,

21:30.110 --> 21:31.970
there is absolutely no such plot.

21:32.270 --> 21:33.560
Could it be that before we came,

21:33.560 --> 21:35.020
there were others like us?

21:36.150 --> 21:38.410
If it really was left by a transmigrator,

21:38.480 --> 21:39.920
there must be other clues nearby.

21:39.750 --> 21:46.710
[SOS]

21:46.920 --> 21:47.780
Noble Consort？

21:49.060 --> 21:51.140
The rain is so heavy today.

21:52.080 --> 21:53.940
Why aren't you using an umbrella?

21:57.050 --> 21:58.120
Crown Prince?

21:58.780 --> 22:00.240
Why are you out here alone?

22:01.770 --> 22:02.690
Your Highness.

22:04.450 --> 22:06.110
I'm here to enjoy the flowers.

22:07.650 --> 22:08.820
Could he also be...

22:09.200 --> 22:10.260
Crown Prince.

22:10.880 --> 22:12.740
In front of my house are two trees.

22:12.830 --> 22:13.830
One is a date tree.

22:14.030 --> 22:15.280
What is the other one?

22:18.890 --> 22:20.270
"Before my bed, the moonlight glows."

22:20.270 --> 22:21.670
Do you know the next line?

22:24.290 --> 22:26.030
-"It looks like frost..."
-Your Highness!

22:26.030 --> 22:27.030
Your Highness!

22:28.350 --> 22:29.790
Greetings, Your Highness.

22:29.790 --> 22:31.960
Your Highness,
I've been looking everywhere for you.

22:31.960 --> 22:33.440
The Empress Dowager is waiting for you.

22:33.440 --> 22:34.270
Your Highness,

22:34.270 --> 22:36.870
I will take His Highness back
to his palace now.

22:49.690 --> 22:50.170
CEO Dan!

22:50.970 --> 22:51.450
CEO Dan!

22:52.810 --> 22:54.560
Guess what I found in the library.

22:54.560 --> 22:54.940
What?

22:57.070 --> 22:58.180
SOS.

23:02.160 --> 23:03.140
SOS?

23:03.600 --> 23:04.200
Yeah.

23:04.750 --> 23:06.010
That distress signal.

23:06.880 --> 23:08.680
I had always been on the 2nd floor before.

23:08.680 --> 23:10.910
Today, I went up to the 3rd floor
to look for books about Yan State.

23:10.910 --> 23:13.470
Through an inconspicuous window,
I happened

23:13.560 --> 23:16.020
to catch sight of an open space
beneath the library.

23:16.020 --> 23:18.030
Someone had planted flowers

23:18.060 --> 23:19.390
spelling out a huge SOS.

23:20.030 --> 23:21.740
So there must be
another transmigrator here

23:21.740 --> 23:22.560
like us.

23:25.200 --> 23:27.120
Could it have been Xie Yong'er?

23:29.380 --> 23:31.180
That's what I thought at first.

23:33.150 --> 23:36.110
But everything she says and does
is written in the book.

23:36.110 --> 23:38.370
There's not a word about asking for help.

23:38.990 --> 23:40.320
It must be someone else.

23:42.420 --> 23:43.950
We've been here for so long.

23:44.180 --> 23:46.040
If there had been anyone strange,

23:46.130 --> 23:47.770
we would have noticed long ago.

23:47.770 --> 23:48.940
What if that person

23:48.970 --> 23:50.760
has been trying hard to hide themselves?

23:50.760 --> 23:52.360
They don't know who to trust,

23:52.500 --> 23:53.650
so they have to use this

23:53.650 --> 23:55.180
subtle way to call for help.

23:56.180 --> 23:56.940
Exactly.

23:57.570 --> 24:00.000
I need to find out
who planted this flower field.

24:00.000 --> 24:00.670
Wait.

24:02.960 --> 24:03.620
Don't rush.

24:04.650 --> 24:06.250
You think it's an SOS signal.

24:06.760 --> 24:07.370
Maybe

24:08.040 --> 24:10.030
the person who planted it
intended it to be

24:10.030 --> 24:11.600
"Two Dragons Playing with a Pearl."

24:11.600 --> 24:12.390
I know.

24:13.420 --> 24:14.180
But what if

24:14.640 --> 24:16.970
there really is someone calling for help?

24:17.630 --> 24:19.110
Just like I was back then.

24:20.490 --> 24:21.710
If I hadn't met you,

24:22.880 --> 24:24.620
I would be so scared struggling alone

24:24.620 --> 24:25.750
in this other world.

24:27.280 --> 24:28.720
Use your imagination.

24:29.420 --> 24:31.080
If we really find that person,

24:31.520 --> 24:32.940
we can play poker.

24:34.010 --> 24:34.840
Do you think

24:35.250 --> 24:36.910
this person is a man or a woman?

24:37.100 --> 24:38.430
Would they like hot pot?

24:39.020 --> 24:40.950
Would they become friends with us?

25:09.240 --> 25:10.040
What's wrong?

25:11.920 --> 25:13.240
I asked around.

25:14.350 --> 25:15.310
They all said

25:16.270 --> 25:17.200
in recent years,

25:17.440 --> 25:19.500
no one has touched that flower field.

25:21.470 --> 25:21.990
See?

25:22.400 --> 25:23.000
I told you.

25:23.960 --> 25:25.420
You were overthinking it.

25:25.880 --> 25:27.030
From a distance,

25:27.400 --> 25:28.270
it really looked like

25:28.270 --> 25:30.150
a miraculous SOS signal.

25:30.830 --> 25:32.430
Then here comes the problem.

25:32.550 --> 25:34.950
These flowers have just started blooming,

25:35.000 --> 25:36.660
and will bloom for a long time.

25:36.960 --> 25:38.830
What if Xie Yong'er passes by one day,

25:38.830 --> 25:39.830
and just like you,

25:40.000 --> 25:41.480
sees the
"Two Dragons Playing with a Pearl"

25:41.480 --> 25:42.590
as an SOS signal?

25:43.310 --> 25:43.790
Guess

25:45.110 --> 25:46.310
what she would think.

25:48.810 --> 25:51.610
She'd also suspect
there's one of her kind nearby.

25:51.750 --> 25:53.550
She might have a sudden epiphany

25:53.960 --> 25:55.330
and suspect us.

25:57.000 --> 25:57.460
Then...

25:57.880 --> 25:59.540
Then we can't keep this field.

26:00.160 --> 26:02.020
Can we find an excuse to remove it?

26:03.110 --> 26:03.680
Please.

26:05.400 --> 26:06.910
Do I need an excuse

26:08.270 --> 26:09.670
for renovating a garden?

26:19.830 --> 26:20.160
What?

26:21.310 --> 26:23.170
Just call it my wild imagination.

26:23.640 --> 26:24.770
I'm still thinking,

26:25.110 --> 26:26.830
what if there really was someone
like us who went through

26:26.830 --> 26:29.920
so much trouble planting all those flowers
to ask for help,

26:29.920 --> 26:31.520
only to get no response at all

26:32.110 --> 26:34.170
and even have the flowers pulled out.

26:35.440 --> 26:37.550
Should we bury something there instead?

26:37.550 --> 26:38.070
Like...

26:38.310 --> 26:39.440
a note or something?

26:41.830 --> 26:44.090
There's a risk Xie Yong'er might find it.

26:45.240 --> 26:45.800
True.

26:49.240 --> 26:51.240
Anyway, the person who planted them

26:51.590 --> 26:53.120
doesn't need them anymore.

26:54.440 --> 26:54.930
What?

26:57.470 --> 26:58.200
I said,

26:59.750 --> 27:01.150
you look so pretty today.

27:06.100 --> 27:06.860
[Promoting Yan millet]

27:06.880 --> 27:08.150
[Commoners: Food]
[Ministry of Revenue: Money]

27:08.150 --> 27:09.420
[Empress Dowager: Power
[Prince Duan: Opposition]

27:12.830 --> 27:15.090
Still thinking about Li Yunxi's method?

27:17.440 --> 27:19.770
I thought he explained it pretty clearly.

27:20.000 --> 27:22.590
There's nothing wrong
with the method itself.

27:22.590 --> 27:24.010
What worries me

27:24.510 --> 27:26.240
is whether it can actually be carried out.

27:26.240 --> 27:27.170
What do you mean?

27:28.200 --> 27:28.680
Look,

27:29.480 --> 27:30.950
back when I was an editor,

27:31.590 --> 27:33.450
for a project to launch smoothly,

27:33.510 --> 27:35.770
it had to satisfy several groups' needs.

27:36.110 --> 27:37.440
The producers want to save money,

27:37.440 --> 27:38.510
the screenwriters want credit,

27:38.510 --> 27:39.920
the directors want artistic freedom,

27:39.920 --> 27:41.720
and the platforms want ratings.

27:41.830 --> 27:44.230
Different positions, different demands.

27:44.590 --> 27:46.000
Only when everyone's needs are met

27:46.000 --> 27:47.800
could the project move forward.

27:49.440 --> 27:50.150
Go on.

27:51.310 --> 27:52.510
So, by the same logic,

27:53.030 --> 27:55.160
to promote the planting of Yan millet,

27:55.570 --> 27:57.900
we have to satisfy several groups at once.

27:58.330 --> 27:59.680
You mean...

28:01.700 --> 28:03.560
The Empress Dowager wants power,

28:03.740 --> 28:05.290
[Empress Dowager: Power]
[Dignity]

28:05.450 --> 28:07.280
so the decree can't come from me.

28:08.260 --> 28:09.860
[Ministry of Revenue: Money]
[Chen Danian]

28:08.460 --> 28:10.120
The Ministry of Revenue has no money,

28:10.120 --> 28:11.940
so the funds must come from elsewhere.

28:11.210 --> 28:12.280
[Commoners: Food][Why plant?]

28:13.960 --> 28:15.290
Prince Duan opposes me,

28:15.720 --> 28:17.520
so I can't be the one benefiting.

28:17.890 --> 28:19.210
Not bad, CEO Dan.

28:19.640 --> 28:20.700
You catch on fast.

28:26.240 --> 28:29.160
This is a place where the finest energies
of heaven and earth converge,

28:29.160 --> 28:31.270
where yin and yang merge.

28:31.880 --> 28:35.200
The dragon veins, surrounding hills,
and water are all perfectly aligned.

28:35.200 --> 28:35.930
The terrain,

28:36.070 --> 28:36.880
momentum,

28:37.070 --> 28:38.390
feng shui, and qi

28:38.480 --> 28:40.140
all are auspicious.

28:40.550 --> 28:41.280
This is...

28:41.350 --> 28:42.380
In other words,

28:43.030 --> 28:44.270
this is the best place

28:45.550 --> 28:46.750
to build a mausoleum?

28:47.640 --> 28:48.270
Exactly.

28:54.880 --> 28:56.740
The Empress Dowager has been

28:56.830 --> 28:58.480
working tirelessly for the state.

28:58.480 --> 29:01.270
Your Majesty,
your wish to build a mausoleum for her

29:01.270 --> 29:04.590
is truly moving.

29:07.510 --> 29:08.590
For many years,

29:10.840 --> 29:13.510
we've been unable to find a suitable site.

29:14.720 --> 29:17.920
Now that the Empress Dowager's birthday
is approaching,

29:19.070 --> 29:20.530
the Imperial Observatory

29:21.400 --> 29:24.330
has identified Mount Bei
as an auspicious location.

29:24.880 --> 29:26.140
I am deeply gratified.

29:28.870 --> 29:30.070
Ministry of Revenue.

29:30.790 --> 29:32.050
Is there enough money?

29:33.400 --> 29:34.400
Well...

29:35.310 --> 29:37.310
Your Majesty,
could you please tell me why?

29:37.310 --> 29:38.840
Did I do something wrong?

29:54.200 --> 29:56.000
Are my eyes playing tricks on me,

29:56.510 --> 29:57.800
or am I seeing a ghost?

29:58.440 --> 29:59.700
Aren't you already...

30:00.500 --> 30:01.300
Your Majesty.

30:01.940 --> 30:02.870
The f-former...

30:03.150 --> 30:06.220
The former Minister of Revenue was my...

30:07.260 --> 30:08.060
twin brother.

30:13.780 --> 30:16.240
It seems the position
of Minister of Revenue

30:17.350 --> 30:19.090
is run by your family.

30:19.550 --> 30:20.550
No, Your Majesty.

30:20.800 --> 30:21.860
It's not like that.

30:21.880 --> 30:22.680
It's just that...

30:22.680 --> 30:24.680
everyone in our Chen family
is willing to serve Great Xia

30:24.680 --> 30:27.370
to our last breath, Your Majesty.

30:28.720 --> 30:29.690
Don't panic.

30:31.030 --> 30:33.090
I won't punish people collectively.

30:33.720 --> 30:36.740
As long as you raise the funds to build
the Empress Dowager's

30:36.740 --> 30:37.730
mausoleum,

30:42.250 --> 30:43.510
I will even reward you.

30:50.550 --> 30:51.980
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

30:51.980 --> 30:53.040
Allow me to report!

30:53.590 --> 30:54.080
Speak.

30:55.090 --> 30:56.660
The mausoleum project is massive,

30:56.660 --> 30:58.620
but the treasury is tight at the moment.

30:58.620 --> 30:59.330
Unless...

31:00.360 --> 31:01.150
Unless what?

31:01.750 --> 31:02.610
We raise taxes!

31:03.240 --> 31:03.960
Raise taxes?

31:03.960 --> 31:04.590
Raise taxes?

31:04.590 --> 31:05.420
How can we do that?

31:05.420 --> 31:06.090
Indeed.

31:08.570 --> 31:12.170
The Ministry of Revenue
proposes raising taxes again this year.

31:12.350 --> 31:13.550
What do you all think?

31:15.590 --> 31:16.050
Well...

31:25.790 --> 31:27.470
Since none of you has reached a decision,

31:27.470 --> 31:28.390
stay here

31:29.550 --> 31:33.210
and discuss it until you reach
a conclusion before the court ends.

31:35.130 --> 31:37.370
Your Majesty.

31:38.060 --> 31:39.150
I heard

31:39.170 --> 31:40.420
that His Majesty
plans to build a mausoleum

31:40.420 --> 31:43.360
at Mount Bei for you as a birthday gift.

31:45.240 --> 31:47.960
I'm both happy and helpless.

31:50.240 --> 31:51.650
How so?

31:51.720 --> 31:52.890
I'm happy

31:52.960 --> 31:55.550
because His Majesty and Your Majesty
share such a deep mother-son bond.

31:55.550 --> 31:57.080
It makes everyone envious.

31:58.480 --> 31:59.960
And the helpless part?

32:01.110 --> 32:02.770
I am helpless because...

32:02.800 --> 32:04.790
the gift from His Majesty is so grand

32:04.790 --> 32:07.000
that anything we give

32:07.020 --> 32:08.620
will seem insignificant.

32:10.640 --> 32:11.980
Flatterer.

32:18.590 --> 32:22.280
Building a mausoleum
wastes money and manpower.

32:23.270 --> 32:26.830
Those who know
see it's the emperor's filial devotion

32:26.830 --> 32:28.160
acting on his own.

32:28.750 --> 32:29.770
Those who don't

32:29.920 --> 32:31.220
might think I

32:31.550 --> 32:33.150
do not care about the people.

32:33.880 --> 32:36.070
The Ministry of Revenue is short on money.

32:36.070 --> 32:37.250
Let's put

32:37.640 --> 32:38.970
this matter aside for now.

32:38.970 --> 32:41.170
Your words are mistaken, Your Majesty.

32:42.850 --> 32:44.020
In every dynasty,

32:44.520 --> 32:46.800
the Empress Dowager's mausoleum
isn't just a tomb—

32:46.800 --> 32:48.620
it represents the royal prestige

32:48.620 --> 32:51.220
and is the highest honor
for women of the harem.

32:51.430 --> 32:52.480
Our Great Xia thrives

32:52.480 --> 32:54.780
and the people prosper

32:55.290 --> 32:57.890
thanks to Your Majesty's
careful management.

32:58.130 --> 32:58.790
Do you

33:00.150 --> 33:03.080
want to be outshone
by the previous Empress Dowager?

33:04.550 --> 33:06.250
You certainly are bold.

33:06.640 --> 33:07.830
I only said

33:07.880 --> 33:09.880
what others want to say but dare not.

33:10.720 --> 33:12.350
The construction of the mausoleum

33:12.350 --> 33:13.880
is known by the whole court.

33:13.980 --> 33:14.950
Stopping it now

33:15.510 --> 33:17.110
would be truly disgraceful.

33:18.350 --> 33:19.150
Your Majesty,

33:19.790 --> 33:21.390
we absolutely can't do this.

33:26.000 --> 33:26.910
Really?

33:27.110 --> 33:27.750
Yes.

33:30.240 --> 33:31.160
Yes, indeed.

33:32.510 --> 33:32.910
Right.

33:35.510 --> 33:37.040
Then tell me,

33:37.830 --> 33:40.830
how should this mausoleum be built?

33:41.960 --> 33:42.270
I...

33:47.830 --> 33:48.580
Make way!

33:48.830 --> 33:50.690
Irrelevant persons, stand back!

34:03.720 --> 34:04.450
Your Majesty!

34:04.450 --> 34:05.000
What are you doing?

34:05.000 --> 34:05.800
Your Majesty!

34:06.160 --> 34:08.090
Your Majesty! I demand to see you!

34:08.710 --> 34:09.480
Your Majesty!

34:09.480 --> 34:10.210
How dare you!

34:10.360 --> 34:12.590
Startling His Majesty
is a capital offense!

34:12.590 --> 34:13.670
I'm dying anyway!

34:14.190 --> 34:15.050
Your Majesty!

34:15.190 --> 34:16.739
Please show mercy!

34:16.920 --> 34:17.960
Otherwise, I will die

34:17.960 --> 34:19.280
with my grievances unresolved!

34:19.280 --> 34:20.590
-Drag him away now!
-Your Majesty!

34:20.590 --> 34:21.510
-Your Majesty!
-Hurry!

34:21.510 --> 34:22.190
Your Majesty!

34:22.190 --> 34:22.800
Your Majesty!

34:22.800 --> 34:23.429
Stop!

34:24.280 --> 34:24.719
Wait.

34:27.630 --> 34:28.280
Let him go.

34:28.960 --> 34:29.560
Let him go!

34:30.510 --> 34:32.480
I am here. If you have any grievance,

34:32.480 --> 34:34.139
tell me everything in detail.

34:36.880 --> 34:37.679
Your Majesty,

34:38.360 --> 34:39.900
please show mercy

34:42.030 --> 34:43.909
and leave us a way to live.

34:47.360 --> 34:48.820
How is there no way to live?

34:53.440 --> 34:54.239
Your Majesty,

34:55.190 --> 34:57.250
you live in luxury within the palace.

34:58.400 --> 35:01.230
Do you know what kind of life
the common people are living?

35:01.230 --> 35:02.800
A single vegetable like this

35:02.800 --> 35:04.130
sells only for one coin,

35:04.360 --> 35:06.360
but taxes take up more than half of it.

35:06.360 --> 35:07.750
After deducting costs,

35:07.920 --> 35:08.920
the actual profit

35:09.670 --> 35:11.030
is less than a tenth.

35:11.320 --> 35:12.970
All my fellow villagers

35:13.550 --> 35:15.280
toil from

35:15.280 --> 35:17.440
dawn to dusk.

35:17.960 --> 35:19.560
Yet after all that labor,

35:20.150 --> 35:22.010
the grain left at year's end

35:22.440 --> 35:24.370
is only enough to stave off hunger.

35:24.480 --> 35:25.150
My...

35:25.590 --> 35:27.250
My younger brother and sister

35:27.360 --> 35:29.590
were born into a year of poor harvest

35:30.280 --> 35:31.480
and starved to death.

35:31.920 --> 35:33.650
They didn't even get the chance

35:35.150 --> 35:36.280
to see this world.

35:42.440 --> 35:43.650
These lines...

35:47.070 --> 35:48.730
My younger brother and sister

35:49.150 --> 35:50.470
were born into

35:50.710 --> 35:53.800
a year of poor harvest
and starved to death.

35:55.480 --> 35:56.280
Your Majesty,

35:56.800 --> 35:59.360
my family
is already struggling to survive.

35:59.860 --> 36:01.850
Now that taxes are rising again,

36:02.070 --> 36:03.750
I fear even my elderly parents

36:06.590 --> 36:07.990
won't be able to survive.

36:17.450 --> 36:19.070
This is driving the common people

36:19.070 --> 36:20.000
to a dead end!

36:20.550 --> 36:21.510
What are you doing?

36:21.510 --> 36:22.760
The mood is just right.

36:22.760 --> 36:23.890
Why did you stand up?

36:23.960 --> 36:25.820
They are driving us to our deaths!

36:27.150 --> 36:28.540
Yes, Your Majesty!

36:28.590 --> 36:30.190
No more tax increases!

36:32.190 --> 36:34.760
Your Majesty, no more tax increases!

36:35.630 --> 36:37.420
How can this be?

36:39.480 --> 36:41.960
Bring the Minister of Revenue to me
at once!

36:42.440 --> 36:43.500
Yes, Your Majesty!

36:48.070 --> 36:51.470
Your Majesty, Chen Danian,
the Minister of Revenue, is here.

36:51.590 --> 36:52.390
Your Majesty!

36:52.400 --> 36:54.000
I am innocent!

36:54.150 --> 36:57.010
Why is the Ministry of Revenue
raising taxes again?

36:57.840 --> 36:58.300
Well...

36:59.670 --> 37:01.230
Didn't Your Majesty want to build

37:01.230 --> 37:03.230
the Empress Dowager's...

37:11.150 --> 37:11.720
Yes.

37:12.590 --> 37:13.800
It was me.

37:14.200 --> 37:15.690
I thought that

37:15.720 --> 37:19.100
building the Empress Dowager's mausoleum
must not be done carelessly,

37:19.100 --> 37:19.740
but...

37:19.890 --> 37:21.690
but there weren't enough funds.

37:21.820 --> 37:22.560
So...

37:22.590 --> 37:23.470
No money?

37:24.810 --> 37:27.190
And with no money, you think you can
take our lives as payment?

37:27.190 --> 37:28.050
Let go!

37:28.480 --> 37:29.470
In that case,

37:29.590 --> 37:30.920
our family has no choice

37:31.510 --> 37:32.960
but to cut off our heads

37:33.040 --> 37:34.570
and offer a bowl of hot blood

37:34.910 --> 37:36.680
to Your Majesty!

37:47.920 --> 37:49.650
"The ruler relies on the state,

37:50.230 --> 37:52.000
and the state relies on the people."

37:52.000 --> 37:53.400
Such a simple truth,

37:54.380 --> 37:56.440
and yet you, the Minister of Revenue,

37:56.800 --> 37:58.000
don't understand it?

37:59.300 --> 38:00.520
I want to ask you,

38:00.880 --> 38:02.810
why are the funds for the mausoleum

38:03.220 --> 38:05.230
not taken from the state treasury?

38:06.310 --> 38:06.830
Well...

38:10.710 --> 38:11.580
I was wrong.

38:12.280 --> 38:13.820
I was wrong!

38:14.600 --> 38:16.260
Take me to the state treasury!

38:16.270 --> 38:18.250
Your Majesty, you cannot go there!

38:18.270 --> 38:19.430
Today, I must...

38:21.400 --> 38:24.330
I must give an explanation
to the people of Great Xia!

38:26.110 --> 38:27.740
Your Majesty is wise!

38:28.280 --> 38:32.190
Your Majesty is wise!
Your Majesty is wise!

38:32.220 --> 38:37.590
Your Majesty is wise!
Your Majesty is wise!

38:56.590 --> 38:57.320
What is it?

38:58.190 --> 38:58.990
Why the panic?

38:59.510 --> 39:00.930
The Emperor publicly berated
the Minister of Revenue

39:00.930 --> 39:02.360
over the tax increase.

39:02.890 --> 39:03.960
Now he's escorting him

39:03.960 --> 39:05.560
to the Ministry's treasury.

39:07.760 --> 39:10.280
He has an ulterior motive.

39:15.150 --> 39:16.030
I knew

39:17.070 --> 39:19.530
building the mausoleum wasn't that simple.

39:19.960 --> 39:21.110
It seems our Emperor

39:22.190 --> 39:24.190
is going after the Empress Dowager.

39:27.550 --> 39:30.210
Since they're putting each other
over the fire,

39:32.880 --> 39:33.730
I might as well

39:38.210 --> 39:39.600
add fuel to the flames.

39:44.840 --> 39:47.250
Zhang San's Diary.

39:47.670 --> 39:51.120
Are there other transmigrators like me?

39:53.670 --> 39:54.620
Wait.

40:01.850 --> 40:02.510
"Yuanfang,

40:03.140 --> 40:04.200
what do you think?"

40:04.260 --> 40:06.110
My name is not Yuanfang.

40:06.250 --> 40:07.700
"I simply cannot do it!"

40:07.910 --> 40:08.530
I...

40:08.550 --> 40:09.880
I am just a servant!

40:11.710 --> 40:13.040
"Imperial Jade Wine.

40:13.230 --> 40:14.430
180 for a cup."

40:14.610 --> 40:16.010
Spare me, Your Highness!

40:18.970 --> 40:19.650
You may go.

40:20.090 --> 40:20.970
Yes.

40:25.170 --> 40:27.890
Where is the female lead

40:28.720 --> 40:30.650
who transmigrated into this book?

40:39.630 --> 40:40.830
I have to find a way

40:40.850 --> 40:42.400
to leave a noticeable mark.

40:43.250 --> 40:44.790
One that only my kind would notice.
